\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf4 \cb3 Epigenetics 
\f1\b0 does not involve modifying the genetic code, but instead the 
\f2\i regulation 
\f1\i0 of when genes are expressed. Epigenetic changes are 
\f0\b heritable
\f1\b0 . Below are some examples of 
\f0\b epigenetic changes
\f1\b0 : \cb1 \
\pard\tx560\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf4 \cb3 \uc0\u9679  \'a0
